msgctxt "mn30:7.2"
msgid "Tamenaṃ cakkhumā puriso disvā evaṃ vadeyya: "
msgstr "If a person with good eyesight saw him they’d say: "

msgctxt "mn30:7.3"
msgid "‘aññāsi vatāyaṃ bhavaṃ puriso sāraṃ, aññāsi phegguṃ, aññāsi tacaṃ, aññāsi papaṭikaṃ, aññāsi sākhāpalāsaṃ. "
msgstr "‘This gentleman knows what heartwood, softwood, bark, shoots, or branches and leaves are. "

