#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya8, sc7
msgctxt "mn30:8.1"
msgid "Evameva kho, brāhmaṇa, idhekacco puggalo saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito hoti: "
msgstr "In the same way, take a certain person who goes forth from the lay life to homelessness, thinking: "

msgctxt "mn30:8.2"
msgid "‘otiṇṇomhi jātiyā jarāya maraṇena sokehi paridevehi dukkhehi domanassehi upāyāsehi, dukkhotiṇṇo dukkhapareto, "
msgstr "‘I’m swamped by rebirth, old age, and death; by sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress. I’m swamped by suffering, mired in suffering. "

msgctxt "mn30:8.3"
msgid "appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethā’ti. "
msgstr "Hopefully I can find an end to this entire mass of suffering.’ "

msgctxt "mn30:8.4"
msgid "So evaṃ pabbajito samāno lābhasakkārasilokaṃ abhinibbatteti. "
msgstr "When they’ve gone forth they generate possessions, honor, and popularity. "

msgctxt "mn30:8.5"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena attamano hoti paripuṇṇasaṅkappo. "
msgstr "They’re happy with that, and they’ve got all they wished for. "

msgctxt "mn30:8.6"
msgid "So tena lābhasakkārasilokena attānukkaṃseti, paraṃ vambheti: "
msgstr "And they glorify themselves and put others down on account of that: "

msgctxt "mn30:8.7"
msgid "‘ahamasmi lābhasakkārasilokavā, ime panaññe bhikkhū appaññātā appesakkhā’ti. "
msgstr "‘I’m the one with possessions, honor, and popularity. These other mendicants are obscure and insignificant.’ "

msgctxt "mn30:8.8"
msgid "Lābhasakkārasilokena ca ye aññe dhammā uttaritarā ca paṇītatarā ca tesaṃ dhammānaṃ sacchikiriyāya na chandaṃ janeti, na vāyamati, olīnavuttiko ca hoti sāthaliko. "
msgstr "They become lazy and slack regarding their possessions, honor, and popularity, not generating enthusiasm or trying to realize those things that are better and finer. … "

msgctxt "mn30:8.9"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, brāhmaṇa, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva sāraṃ atikkamma phegguṃ atikkamma tacaṃ atikkamma papaṭikaṃ, sākhāpalāsaṃ chetvā ādāya pakkanto ‘sāran’ti maññamāno. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn30:8.10"
msgid "Yañcassa sārena sārakaraṇīyaṃ tañcassa atthaṃ nānubhavissati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn30:8.11"
msgid "Tathūpamāhaṃ, brāhmaṇa, imaṃ puggalaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "They’re like the person who mistakes branches and leaves for heartwood, I say. "

